channel.title: Terecraft(Premium)Anarchy 1.2.5 24/7 Dedicated
channel.description:
Terecraft 24/7 Premium 1.3, PvP/Anarchy, Factions, MCMMO, Economy raiding server!
Terecraft provides great 24/7 premium PvP anarchy gameplay with little to NO LAG! Joining factions and creating them is also permitted. Alongside server economy, MCMMO and raiding / griefing! There are cool donation benefits on the server, such as ranks, items and simple donations, donations help improve and run the server and award you with packages.
Join today and enjoy some of the best plugins, players and a great community! We also have a forums at www.terecraft.org, register today and become one of our great players! See you in game at IP = terecraft.us15.creeperhost.net!
